{"tha-ap161:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap161:0.2":"Bandhujivakavagga ","tha-ap161:0.3":"Punnagapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap161:1.1":"“Kananam vanamogayha, ","tha-ap161:1.2":"vasami luddako aham; ","tha-ap161:1.3":"Punnagam pupphitam disva, ","tha-ap161:1.4":"buddhasettham anussarim. ","tha-ap161:2.1":"Tam puppham ocinitvana, ","tha-ap161:2.2":"sugandham gandhitam subham; ","tha-ap161:2.3":"Thupam karitva puline, ","tha-ap161:2.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap161:3.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap161:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap161:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap161:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap161:4.1":"Ekamhi navute kappe, ","tha-ap161:4.2":"eko asim tamonudo; ","tha-ap161:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap161:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap161:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap161:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap161:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap161:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma punnagapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap161:7.1":"Punnagapupphiyattherassapadanam navamam. "}